{"tid":163783,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"培正中學學生不畏食肉菌   體驗赤腳行街市","createTime":"2017-03-20T08:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T11:05:52.000Z","uid":36383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"486c6445bdd8906d4634c9167987aebf5b0ae1b5","tid":163783,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T08:51:50.000Z","msg":"培正中學校長譚日旭回覆東網查詢時指，日營活動包括赤腳步行體驗，旨在希望學生體驗一些在日常生活少有的經歷，讓學生走出舒適區。他表示，會了解及檢討活動的安排，包括是否繼續使用該模式舉辦活動，而學校亦會做風險評估，確保學生在安全情況下進行教學活動。"},{"pid":"08b8475fd8055cf0fb4864b5a3eff018dfff60f9","tid":163783,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T08:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗乜做風險評估 最大風險咪食肉菌"},{"pid":"30ac797f85c5c8e9065eedabeed962acf768433a","tid":163783,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T08:54:41.000Z","msg":"食下橙皮咪算囉啊校長"},{"pid":"405277e4e9f52221787fd3313d0cee34db549548","tid":163783,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T08:58:17.000Z","msg":"以前都有類似活動<br />\n不過係自願參與性質+喺行人路<br />\n依家呢個係強制+街市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a966a7728004882e4269ad239add73d9e4dd071","tid":163783,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:00:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗乜做風險評估 最大風險咪食肉菌</blockquote><br />\n奶左菌入血<br />\n好似要切腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116aa7014580ab141218f744201d7ec1a711eac8","tid":163783,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗乜做風險評估 最大風險咪食肉菌</blockquote><br />\n奶左菌入血<br />\n好似要切腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n切腳都未必醫到"},{"pid":"531f8de0e94556ba726f800d090bb50d8b626fd2","tid":163783,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前都有類似活動<br />\n不過係自願參與性質+喺行人路<br />\n依家呢個係強制+街市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲活動都痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4337f99f9948be3db653ea2e1ded515b12c0e7d5","tid":163783,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗乜做風險評估 最大風險咪食肉菌</blockquote><br />\n奶左菌入血<br />\n好似要切腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n切腳都未必醫到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔一定<br />\n輕則切肉植皮啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b12d9facfa419b2b6582c16873b24e37733ec4e","tid":163783,"uid":76933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:09:39.000Z","msg":"食肉菌係咪好罕見? <br />\n如果常見咪死好多豬肉佬賣魚佬? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34433db8828eedd8af2ee205b7bf80b881933612","tid":163783,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食肉菌係咪好罕見? <br />\n如果常見咪死好多豬肉佬賣魚佬? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n著哂水鞋架WO<br />\n<br />\n創傷弧菌是一種常活於和暖海水的細菌。若傷口接觸海水，或進食被該細菌污染的食物，可引致感染。<br />\n<br />\n所以有傷口唔好游水<br />\n<br />\n游既話就冇左一兩隻手腳"},{"pid":"58c2b018bcb66241ffc4752422c1f610b794a3ea","tid":163783,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:26:24.000Z","msg":"預防創傷弧菌感染，尤其是一些患有免疫系統疾病及長期病患者，應注意下列事項：<br />\n前往街市時，避免皮膚接觸污水。<br />\n<br />\n培正學生仲好揪過基道中學D學生,無畏無懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e97d5d12bcda54aeddf2a2decc8555b1e735f5f","tid":163783,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:29:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>攞命食肉菌潛伏　街市買餸中招<br />\n竹籮割傷　男子截肢危殆</strong><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】街市隨時成為死亡陷阱。一名男子在土瓜灣市政大廈街市買餸時，不小心被竹籮割傷兩條小腿後，疑因此<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">感染食肉菌</span></span></strong>中的創傷弧菌引致壞死性筋膜炎，需<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">切除一雙小腿保命</span></span></strong>。據悉，他出現<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">腎、心臟及呼吸衰竭，情況危殆</span></span>。有傳染病專科醫生表示，創傷弧菌常存在於海水，街市中用來盛載海產的竹籮等器皿或地上的海水都可能含菌，市民到街市時要小心。"},{"pid":"6dbdd19bfa42e1c7d82b43a6cae003942056c1ff","tid":163783,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:29:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>攞命食肉菌潛伏　街市買餸中招<br />\n竹籮割傷　男子截肢危殆</strong><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】街市隨時成為死亡陷阱。一名男子在土瓜灣市政大廈街市買餸時，不小心被竹籮割傷兩條小腿後，疑因此<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">感染食肉菌</span></span></strong>中的創傷弧菌引致壞死性筋膜炎，需<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">切除一雙小腿保命</span></span></strong>。據悉，他出現<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">腎、心臟及呼吸衰竭，情況危殆</span></span>。有傳染病專科醫生表示，創傷弧菌常存在於海水，街市中用來盛載海產的竹籮等器皿或地上的海水都可能含菌，市民到街市時要小心。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20100608/14112196\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20100608%2F14112196&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=e85bd986\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20100608%2F14112196&h=980f6a5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20100608/14112196</a>"},{"pid":"f5cb19b874d99fb0c853b04ea8cb4ae620beab7f","tid":163783,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:50:31.000Z","msg":"配合一帶一路，將學生送往敘利亞和伊拉克等戰區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362a88d192aeccd6a8fa54ae44d456641c7f4b29","tid"